00:49:39,935 --> 00:49:43,020
Mr. Zuckerbert,
habe ich Ihre volle Aufmerksamkeit?

985
00:49:43,855 --> 00:49:44,939
Nein.

986
00:49:46,024 --> 00:49:47,400
